description:
Angus MacGyver (Richard Dean Anderson) is the Phoenix Foundation’s most resourceful agent, a problem-solver who relies on science and quick thinking instead of weapons. Whether he’s blocking gunmen with a mop, using an emergency hose as a zip line, or fixing a broken boat with branches and a tarp, MacGyver always finds a clever way out of danger with whatever he has on hand.

Stream MacGyver (1985) on Paramount+.
